org.tensorics.core.commons.lang

Interface OngoingOperation<T,V>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - defines the type of the input/result main tensoric object
    V - defines the type of possible value interaction of the main tensoric object. In another words it is the tensor value.
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    OngoingDeferredQuantifiedTensorOperation, OngoingDeferredTensorOperation, OngoingQuantifiedTensorBackedOperation, OngoingQuantifiedTensorOperation, OngoingTensorBackedOperation, OngoingTensorOperation

    public interface OngoingOperation<T,V>
    The top interface that defines all required common operations in the tensorics world.
